Big thanks to all the amazing Linkle mod creators out there — you’re absolute angels! &lt;br data-start="212" data-end="215"&gt;&#13;
This version is based on &lt;strong data-start="240" data-end="268"&gt;VincentVonDarkness’s mod&lt;/strong&gt;, with further adjustments to give &lt;strong data-start="303" data-end="325"&gt;The Linkle Mod 3.0&lt;/strong&gt; two completely distinct styles.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
To make Linkle blend more naturally into the world of Hyrule, I fine-tuned her facial features for a more human and lifelike look: thicker eyebrows, fuller lips (a touch of sensuality to make her feel more vivid — just my personal interpretation), subtle neck shading to enhance depth, and underwear adjustments for a more balanced visual effect.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&lt;hr data-start="711" data-end="714"&gt;&#13;
&lt;strong data-start="716" data-end="758"&gt;Ancient Memories Version — Sonia Style&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br data-start="758" data-end="761"&gt;&#13;
Inspired by the ancient Zonai motifs, this version features blonde hair, thin eyebrows, green eyes, fuller lips, neck shading, a neutral skin tone, and updated underwear for a more harmonious look.&lt;br data-start="958" data-end="961"&gt;&#13;
(Currently still working on fixing issues with HD texture replacement and model mapping errors.)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&lt;hr data-start="1061" data-end="1064"&gt;&#13;
&lt;strong data-start="1066" data-end="1095"&gt;Spirit of Freedom Version&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br data-start="1095" data-end="1098"&gt;&#13;
Black hair, thick eyebrows, brown eyes, fuller lips, neck shading, and a warm tan skin tone.&lt;br data-start="1190" data-end="1193"&gt;&#13;
Underwear adjusted for better visual balance — a more grounded, natural, and expressive Linkle. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
