      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68fa2e7b33771.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68f8ea55abb09.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68f8ea68d2096.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68fa2f0ca0c19.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68fa1e87c5293.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68fa2f2f2ccf4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68f8ea4a4b2ca.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68fa1f2fa907a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68fa2fa447c75.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a major fix and re-upload of &lt;b&gt;The Lone Devil's iconic Elite Knight Set&lt;/b&gt; mod for &lt;i&gt;The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild&lt;/i&gt; (CEMU).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;This mod package brings the gear of the Elite Knight to Hyrule, specifically replacing the following default Link items:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Armor:&lt;/b&gt; The &lt;b&gt;Elite Knight Set&lt;/b&gt; (Helm, Armor, Gauntlets, Leggings) replaces the entire &lt;b&gt;Dark Link Armor Set&lt;/b&gt; (Tunic, Trousers, Hood).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Weapon:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;Astora's Straight Sword&lt;/b&gt; replaces the &lt;b&gt;Knight Broadsword&lt;/b&gt; model.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Shield:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;Crest Shield&lt;/b&gt; replaces the &lt;b&gt;Knight Shield&lt;/b&gt; model.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;This updated package resolves two critical issues from the original mod:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ol start="1"&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Missing Model/Transparency Fix:&lt;/b&gt; The original model had an issue where the &lt;b&gt;left shoulder armor piece ('soldier') appeared transparent/invisible&lt;/b&gt; due to incomplete 3D model geometry. This version includes the &lt;b&gt;fully completed and visible model&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;BCML Compatibility:&lt;/b&gt; The file structure has been corrected and adjusted to be &lt;b&gt;installed properly using the latest versions of BCML&lt;/b&gt; (BotW Cemu Mod Loader), resolving the persistent installation failures previously reported (e.g., with game dumps from gamebana.com).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;i class="SelectedElement"&gt;Credit for the original armor model goes to &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1633179"&gt;The Lone Devil&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/i&gt; Enjoy an iconic, bug-free journey as the Chosen Undead in Hyrule!&lt;br&gt;</description>
