      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 16:24:45 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65179f83ef3eb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65179f968c531.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685cd131b652.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6517a0bcea4d5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6517a0c826817.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6517a0c86635d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6517a0c84fd1e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d28da0a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d290a5e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d2a97be.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d2bd141.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d2d69ed.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d2d4e60.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d2dba2f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d2e8f08.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d2e7f10.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6685d5d3a92f6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Frostbite Armor fix&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed an issue where the Frostbite Armor's right hand would deform while using the restored arm mop pack&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Here is an early version of the Tears of the Kingdom overhaul of Breath of the Wild. I have added the almost every Armor in the bnp. I have also made a verions that has thr right  arm Restored. I have replaced Link's default hair with his TOTK long hair, the physics are not perfect but for now they will do. I have also added the hairband, which is temporarily located in one of the chests in the Shrine of resurrection. Also, I have added the default armor for Link which basically only changes the underwear and Link's Upper model! I was able to give it a material that gives the arm emission. I have also made changes to most of the Chest armor pieces to make it just like in TOTK, but for some armors like the past link armors, I did not want to change them, if you guys want me to, I will, but if not I won't. For now, that's all that this mod offers. I am planning to replace the overworld themes for TOTK as well as the enemy models too, so if anyone wants to join this mod's development, please reach out to me, it's dying cause it gets boring for me at times. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;To do: Some physics and actors (which can take long sometimes due to typos...). There is still missing many updgrade actors as I've not made much progress on the physics side of things. If you have any questions or ideas, let me know!</description>
